<div class="section blue">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="two-third">
			<h1>The Truly Open Payments Protocol</h1>
			<p>The Hyper Ledger Transaction Protocol (HLTP) is protocol designed from the ground up to enable payments for the internet age. With decentralised nodes running in multiple geographies and jurisdictions, hyperledger provides an amazingly quick, reliable and secure way to record transfers of assets such as digital currencies across the world within seconds, not minutes.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="one-third">
			<div class="row bullet"><span class="twitter social"></span> Lightweight - Designed for simplicity and speed</div>
			<div class="row bullet"><span class="twitter social"></span> Open - Not controlled by a single company</div>
			<div class="row bullet"><span class="twitter social"></span> Equal - No special denominated currency </div>
			<div class="row bullet"><span class="twitter social"></span> Fair - No pre-mining or allocations</div>
			<div class="row bullet"><span class="twitter social"></span> Efficient - No energy intensive proof of work</div>
			<div class="row bullet"><span class="twitter social"></span> Fast - Capable of processing thousands of transactions per second</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
